programme.title: Memori: Wau Itu Bulan
programme.desc: Kisah Pak Seman yang mahir membuat wau namun tiada seorang pun ahli keluarga mahu mewarisi bakatnya itu. Bidin ingin belajar membuat wau dengan Pak Seman tetapi takut berjumpa Pak Seman kerana Pak Seman berwajah garang. Kakak Bidin, Hasnah telah dtg berjumpa Pak Seman untuk memberitahu minat adiknya itu. Hasnah pula berbakat bermain Mak Yong namun tidak disukai oleh emaknya, Kalsom kerana kisah lama arwah suaminya. Kalsom tidak mahu Bidin dan Hasnah mewarisi bakat seni arwah suaminya. Dia mahu mereka menumpukan perhatian pada pelajaran. Kak Yam telah memujuk Kalsom untuk membenarkan Hasnah masuk pertandingan Mak Yong. Hasnah berjaya dalam pertandingan itu. Manakala Bidin berjaya dalam pertandingan wau yang telah direka olehnya sendiri.

programme.title: Panggung RTM : Rentap
programme.desc: Kisah seorang kakak iaitu Farah membesarkan dua orang adiknya iaitu Mizi dan Ain setelah kematian ayahnya. Farah terpaksa menangguhkan hasratnya untuk belajar di universiti demi memastikan Mizi dan Ain ke sekolah. Mizi suka ponteng sekolah dan selalu berlumba haram. Ain pula yang enggan tinggal di asrama suka keluar bersama kawan-kawan dan ponteng sekolah. Farah bekerja di klinik untuk menampung mereka adik-beradik. Mizi dan ain tidak suka dengan sikap Farah yang suka memarahi mereka dan memaksa mereka ke sekolah. Pak long dan mak long selalu membantu Farah dan memberi nasihat padanya. Mizi berkawan dengan Zul yang mengajarnya merompak. Mizi suka kerana dapat duit banyak. Farah meninggal dunia ketika di rompak Mizi.

programme.title: Iris Wanita
programme.desc: Setiap pekerjaan mesti akan ada cabaran masing-masing, dari segi mental dan juga fizikal. Ia lebih mencabar apabila perlu merawat anjing yg dibawa ke klinik tempat dia bertugas. Dikecam itu perkara biasa baginya, namun setiap pekerjaan dan rawatan yg diberi akan dirujuk kpd ustaz dan ulama yg lebih arif tentang tataterbit dan hukum. Malah kerjaya Dr Ima menjadi inspirasi kpd org ramai utk mendalami dunia kesihatan haiwan bersama tetamu jemputan Dr Salehatul Khuzaimah Mohamad Ali Doktor Perubatan Veterinar (DVM, UPM) dalam #IrisWanita

Sementara itu, hari yang penuh dengan pengembaraan dan ketegangan menanti Ezgi dan zgr, yang jatuh di pulau terbiar akibat masalah yang mereka alami, dan rakan serta keluarga mereka yang tidak dapat menghubungi mereka sedang mencari mereka di merata tempat dengan panik.

Ia mengisahkan tiga orang pemuda - Gunung, Daik dan Bercabang - yang melarikan diri daripada menjadi hamba abdi kepada Orang Kaya Seri Bentan. Mereka bertiga berhenti di sebuah kota bernama Lang Buana di pinggir sebuah sungai. Terperangkap oleh keadaan, ketiga-tiga pemuda berkenaan terpaksa menyamar menjadi putera raja dan merangka taktik peperangan bagi memperkuatkan benteng pertahanan Lang Buana.

Dato Bakri bapa kepada Yasmin dan Datin Rosnah ibu kepada Hakim akan berkahwin. Dalam kes berasingan, Mazlan telah ditangkap oleh orang-orang bodyguard Farish. Dia diberi amaran supaya tidak memaparkan gambar bogel Kasandra. Mazlan diberhentikan kerja sebagai Pengurus Kasandra. programme.desc: Satu siri kematian dan kehilangan kejam membawa kembali kepada legenda bandar tentang badut pembunuh bersiri. Sekumpulan pelajar kolej akan menghadapi mimpi ngeri terburuk mereka, apabila Badut jahat ini kembali dari masa lalu pada Halloween.

Apabila kerajaan Thai mengumumkan rancangan untuk mengosongkan bilik kebalnya untuk membayar balik pinjaman IMFnya, sekumpulan Mafia tempatan membuat satu skim untuk rompakan mega, mereka akan mencuri rizab emas negara. Mereka mengupah Navin yang terkenal, bekas pembunuh tentera, untuk mengetuai operasi yang melibatkan semua pencuri terkemuka di negara ini.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Episod 4 mengisahkan Dina diminta Mariam untuk menggoda Rafiq dan berkahwin dengannya. Semasa keluar makan malam dengan Dina, Rafiq ternampak bayang Sarakit dalam kereta. Pada malam yang sama, Mariam sekali lagi diganggu penjelmaan Sarakit dan Mariam berada dalam ketakutan. Mariam mendesak Rafiq meninggalkan Sarakit yang dikatakan mengamalkan ilmu sihir. Rafiq enggan mempercayai kata-kata ibunya dan pulang ke Sarakit. Di rumah, Sarakit tidak kelihatan dan Rafiq berihat di sofa setelah membeli bahanbahan makanan. Sarakit telah memasak untuk Rafiq dan mengingatkan Rafiq janjinya iaitu tidak akan meninggalkan Sarakit. Sarakit kemudiannya menuduh Rafiq berlaku curang dan Rafiq menafikannya. Rafiq menyakinkan Sarakit bahawa dia hanya mencintai Sarakit seorang sahaja. Rafiq terjaga dan mendapati apa yang berlaku antaranya dan Sarakit hanyalah mimpi

programme.title: Project Wolf Hunting
programme.desc: Membawakan penjenayah berbahaya di atas kapal kargo yang diangkut dari Filipina ke Korea Selatan, dimana mereka melepaskan kuasa jahat ketika percubaan melarikan diri membawa kepada rusuhan.

programme.title: 3AM Ep1
programme.desc: Pesta Hantu Lapar sudah hampir. Seorang pekerja baru di telah menyinggung perasaan hantu di bangunan pejabatnya kerana dia tidak hormat kepada roh pada hari pertamanya bekerja. Semasa menjalani syif malam, Lelaki itu dan rakan sekerjanya yang bekerja lebih masa mengalami pertemuan menyeramkan yang membuatkan mereka merenung tingkah laku dan kepercayaan mereka.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep12
programme.desc: Episod 10 memaparkan kisah bagaimana rahsia Hariman, Salim dan Sohot terlibat dalam rompakan batu permata terbongkar apabila Haikal terdengar perbualan mereka. Sementara itu ibu Maira yang pada mulanya teruja apabila diberitahu batu milik Maira bernilai RM 15 ribu bertukar kecewa setelah mendapat tahu batu itu palsu. Manakala Hariman dilihat mengekori dan mengintip setiap pergerakan Imran, Haikal dan Maira.

programme.title: Guardian
programme.desc: Semasa Perang Dingin, sebuah organisasi yang dipanggil "Patriot" mencipta skuad superhero, yang merangkumi ahli-ahli beberapa republik Soviet. Selama bertahun-tahun, wira terpaksa menyembunyikan identiti mereka, tetapi dalam masa sukar mereka mesti menunjukkan diri mereka semula.

programme.title: Conjuring Spirit
programme.desc: Apabila berpindah ke apartmen baharu, seorang ibu dan anak lelakinya yang berusia 5 tahun terus dihantui oleh hantu yang marah bersembunyi di dalam kotak muzik.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep12
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ryan diupah sebagai bodyguard kepada Yasmin oleh bapanya. Yasmin dilarang dari berjumpa dengan Hakim kerana ibu Hakim mempunyai sejarah silam yang menyakitkan dengan bapa Yasmin. Dalam kes berasingan, Rahul telah diupah oleh Datin untuk mengintip kegiatan Dato Rahman. Dato dikatakan mempunyai skandal dengan perempuan lain. Nasha telah meminta Danial menjaga Harris yang selalu diganggu oleh along. Danial mendapati Harris menjadi penjamin kepada rakannya Anuar untuk meminjam wang along tetapi tidak membayar balik wang tersebut. Anuar memberitahu wang tersebut telah dirompak, mereka telah diarahkan oleh Nasha membuat laporan polis. Sementara itu, hubungan Farish dengan Nasha kembali pulih.

programme.title: TABU: Mengusik Gerbang Iblis
programme.desc: Mengisahkan sekumpulan 6 orang sahabat muda yang secara tidak sengaja memasuki hutan larangan di Leuweung Hejo. Mereka ialah Diaz, Keyla, Tio , Adis, Muti dan Mahir. Selepas memasuki hutan, mereka menjalankan aktiviti yang dianggap pantang larang.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep4
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Adam, Shah dan Danial tiga pemuda di sebuah kampung yang baru balik belajar dalam bidang kejuruteraan dari Jepun. Akibat masalah sukar mendapat pekerjaan Adam telah membeli alat pengesan lembaga bersama-sama dengan alat pengesan, alat penyedut serta alatan yang berkaitan tujuan untuk mengesan dan menangkap lembaga yang merupakan lembaga-lembaga yang sesekali masih wujud dan mengganggu manusia atau keluarga. Ibu-ibu mereka juga tidak senang hati yang mereka tidak ada kerja dan mencebur diri dengan kerja tersebut. Dalam pada itu hasil kerja mereka menjadi tersohor dan tersebar dalam akhbar tempatan. Sementara itu Encik Bad, seorang pengusaha muzium lembaga-lembaga dan anak gadisnya telah berpindah ke rumah baru mereka. Cuma setiap malam kedua-dua mereka mengalami gangguan dipercayai daripada lembaga yang belum dikenal pasti.

programme.title: Ong Bak: Muay Thai Warriors
programme.desc: Apabila kepala patung yang suci di sebuah kampung dicuri, seorang ahli seni mempertahankan diri pergi ke bandar besar dan mendapati dirinya mengambil dunia bawah tanah untuk mendapatkannya.

Perbuatan Dina ini terbongkar apabila dia meninggal dunia. Rafiq telah diberitahu Ustaz Hambali bahawa Sarakit yang tinggal bersamanya selama ini adalah Dina yang tidak mengetahui bahawa Sarakit telah lama meninggal dunia. Pada masa yang sama, Mariam telah merayu kepada majikan Rafiq untuk menukarkan Rafiq balik ke Kuala Lumpur. Haris, yang ditugaskan menggantikan tempat Rafiq, telah diganggu lembaga Sarakit semasa dalam perjalanan ke tempat Rafiq. Ramdi pula telah mengambil keputusan untuk meninggalkan kampung kerana tidak tahan dengan gangguan hantu Sarakit.

programme.desc: Tiada tempat untuk dituju, Hairani menaiki sebuah bas ekspres yang dipandu oleh Pie dan Maidin. Setelah itu, Hairani diterima bekerja sebagai salah satu konduktor bersama mereka yang lain. Kehidupannya berubah sekelip mata.

programme.desc: Mat Som ialah seorang penulis bebas yang bekerja di Kuala Lumpur dan tidak banyak mendapat tugasan dan kecewa kerana tidak mendapat buah fikiran untuk meningkatkan tahap kehidupannya. Selain itu dia gagal menarik perhatian gadis sebelah rumah yang diminatinya, Yam. Dia semakin tertekan apabila bapanya memperkenalkannya kepada Wan Faridah.

programme.title: Penyu
programme.desc: Yan, Abu, Yus dan Man diupah pakcik mereka, Chal untuk menjadi pemandu pelancong. Wazir, ketua kumpulan penunggang motosikal dan anaknya, Wati ingin membantu mereka untuk mempromosikan chalet milik pakcik mereka. Cappolla inginkan chalet tersebut untuk dijadikan kelab bagi melindungi kegiatan pelacuran. Mereka cuba untuk menghalang Cappolla namun terperangkap.

programme.desc: Comat tinggal dengan bapanya yang membuka perniagaan membaiki kereta. Pada suatu hari, Borhan menghantar keretanya ke bengkel Pak Comat untuk dibaiki. Di Kuala Lumpur, pelbagai perkara lucu terjadi.

programme.desc: Primary school teacher Lok is a recovering schizophrenic who falls in love with a young girl he first met. As he struggles to reveal his illness, Lok has a relapse and becomes delusional. Little does he know she is a mental health counsellor who has a hidden agenda. The pair develops a relationship that is beyond their wildest dreams.

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: Wu Xia
programme.desc: Martial artist Liu hides his identity and lives in a remote village with his wife Ah Yu and their two sons, but somehow gets embroiled in a bizarre murder case. Constable Xu is a kung fu fanatic, whose curiosity forces Liu into a death duel with the Sect Leader of the 72 Demons, and puts Lius family and homeland in a great danger...

programme.title: Naked Soldier
programme.desc: When Interpol agent Long busted a billion-dollar drug deal 15 years ago, the cartel took revenge and killed his family. The cartel boss, Madame Rose, even kidnaps and raises Longs daughter, Phoenix, to become a skilled assassin. Only when Phoenix is about to kill Long did she discover the startling fact about her true identity

programme.title: Red Line
programme.desc: A former professional car racer, Le falls into despair after causing his brother's death in a car race, until he meets female doctor Hui and becomes an ambulance driver who vows to save lives with speed. Meanwhile, the truth about his brothers accident emerges with the investigation of Le's three good friends...

programme.title: Mr & Mrs Incredible
programme.desc: Middle-aged and retired superhero couple, Huan (Gazer Man) and Red (Aroma Woman), settles into a contented life in a remote village. They find it hard to contain their powers though, and are bored by the uneventful life. When they hear a world martial arts contest is to be held in their village, both are itching to make their long-awaited comeback!

programme.title: Infernal Affairs III
programme.desc: Ming is transferred to do menial police work ten months after the murder of Yan, in 2004. Meanwhile, a new star, Wing, has emerged in the police force and Ming suspects he is also a mole sent by the triad. Determined to start anew, Ming must kill Wing while ensuring his own identity does not get exposed.

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of The Way We Dance features the plight of Hong Kongs grassroots performing artists as they fight against the governments plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Those Were the Days
programme.desc: Director Wong despises Cantonese movies of the 60s, but accidentally travels back in time to that movie set. He meets Director Chu, who tells him he can return to modern time if someone likes the film he makes. Wong meets four classic movie stars and invites them to star in his new film, but it flops unexpectedly. Can Wong return to the present?

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kits master, Debo.

programme.title: Mama's Affair
programme.desc: Former talent manager Mei Fung stays home to take care of her husband and son after retirement. She decides to re-enter the entertainment business to find her value in life, and successfully transforms a local restaurant delivery boy, Fong Ching, into a young pop idol. This makes her teenage son, Jonathan, intensely jealous of Fong Ching.

programme.title: Legally Declared Dead
programme.desc: Insurance agent Sean visits Tak and Ling's home to follow up on a case and is shocked to see their son's corpse hanging above him. He suspects them of murdering their son to claim the insurance money and decides to launch his own investigation. As he becomes obsessed over their guilt, his kind nature is used against him by the real perpetrator.

programme.title: Mr McDreamy
programme.desc: A second generation rich man squanders his parents money and calls himself Mr McDreamy. When his parents finally have enough and cut him off financially, he establishes a Mr McDreamy Training Academy using various unconventional means to transform his four recruits into Mr McDreamies with hilarious results.

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Secret Diary of a Mom To Be, The
programme.desc: A high-flying PR manager and her loving husband swear by a childless lifestyle but she is shocked to learn that she is expecting just when things look bright for a promotion! How would they deal with the unexpected surprises that life throws in their way?

programme.title: Fist of Legend
programme.desc: When Chen Zhen studies in Japan, he finds several Chinese students missing and accidentally uncovers the Black Dragon Societys conspiracy. A new drug is invented to boost bodies of the Japanese troops in war and the Chinese students are used in their experiments. Chen Zhen vows to take down the evil society and destroy their secret laboratory.

programme.title: Golden Job
programme.desc: A group of former mercenaries reunite to plan an epic heist: boosting a truckload of medicine held by a foreign intelligence agency to supply a refugee camp in need. When they find the truck is filled with stolen gold however, they realize they have been double-crossed by one of their own and putting the situation right will be an all-out war.

programme.title: Love is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, she is left alone at home when her husband is away on a work trip. An intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. As Bo tries to survive his mental and psychological torture, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to the accident leading to her blindness

Chow Mo Wan encounters many women in his life but is touched by none after he lost his true love. Following an encounter one day, he decides to write a fiction titled 2046 which takes place at Room 2046. Nothing ever changes at Room 2046, and people go there to find their lost memories.

programme.title: All's Well End's Well 2012
programme.desc: This beloved slapstick comedy series continues as it follows four couples who meet through a dating website. Four men go on a heroic mission to help four women and wind up experiencing a series of mishaps.

programme.title: The Lady Improper
programme.desc: Siu Man is divorced by her husband due to her fear of intimacy. After that, she wants to restart her life by taking over her fathers restaurant. Siu Man hires a new chef with unique culinary philosophy that revitalizes her. Tired of the shackles she placed on herself, Siu Man embarks on a journey of self-discovery and sexual liberation.

programme.title: Two Tigers
programme.desc: This crime comedy is about a bumbling young man Fang Nan, who kidnaps a middle-aged businessman Zhang Cheng Gong for ransom. However, the captor becomes the captive when Zhang turns the tables on Fang and forces him to complete three tasks. The two men soon find themselves sharing a journey filled with absurdity and deception.

programme.title: Love is Cold
programme.desc: In the mid-1990s in Macau, a teenage boy and girl kill someone and clean up the crime scene together. The girl is from China and is bullied in her new school. The boy is from a complicated family who has close ties to the gangster world. They are instantly attracted to each other when they met but who did they kill and will they get away with it?

programme.title: Fist of Legend
programme.desc: When Chen Zhen studies in Japan, he finds several Chinese students missing and accidentally uncovers the Black Dragon Societys conspiracy. A new drug is invented to boost bodies of the Japanese troops in war and the Chinese students are used in their experiments. Chen Zhen vows to take down the evil society and destroy their secret laboratory.

programme.title: Ride On
programme.desc: Master Luo, a washed-up stuntman, trains his beloved horse Red Hare to be a stunt horse. Due to his debts though, Red Hare may be taken away by the debtors. Master Luo has no choice but to seek help from his estranged daughter, and the incident ends up becoming a golden opportunity for them to reconcile.

programme.title: Bodyguards and Assassins
programme.desc: On 15 October 1906, Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat Sen returned to Hong Kong to stage another overthrow of the Qing dynasty. Businessman Lee and Chinese Dailys Chief Chan arrange for five bodyguards to protect Mr Sun - these are all extraordinary fighters who are ready and up for fierce battles against the Qing assassination army.

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Polices Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: The Sunny Side of the Street
programme.desc: Hassan is a Pakistani refugee boy whose father has died in a car accident. A local taxi driver, Yat, then helps him flee Hong Kong. In the process, the two gradually develop a father-son relationship, until Hassan discovers the shocking truth about his fathers death

programme.title: Kung Fu Monster
programme.desc: In the Ming Dynasty, the Bruneian Empire offers a monster as a gift to the nation. Imperial guard Ocean is tasked to train it, but realizing it is a kind creature by nature, he releases it secretly so that it will not become a killing beast. His action prompts a frenzy hunt for the monster when the palace puts a hefty bounty for its return

programme.title: The Captain
programme.desc: The movie is based on a real incident of Sichuan Airlines Flight 8633 on 14 May 2018. When the cockpit windshield shatters after takeoff, the Captain manages to land the airplane safely with his level-headed swift actions and sheer determination. This is lauded as a miracle in airline history.

programme.title: My Name Ain'T Suzie
programme.desc: Young Mei Li works as a bar girl in Wanchai to make a living. When she meets Jimmy in the bar, she thinks he is her true love and falls crazily in love with him. When Jimmy has to leave, Mei Li is devastated. It is not until she encounters the triad boss Ying that she finally found someone to count on.

programme.title: The Black Enforcer
programme.desc: Lung the Black Enforcer is ordered to escort a murderer Fei to prison. While taking shelter in Lungs house from the snowstorm, Fei is rescued by his gang and Fei kills Lungs mother and sister before escaping. Lung is imprisoned for the failed task and after being released, he vows to avenge his family by killing Fei.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: Heroes Of The East
programme.desc: A Chinese man marries a Japanese woman through an arranged marriage and manages to insult all of her Japanese martial arts family by issuing a challenge to her that is misinterpreted by the others. He must then prove how good Chinese Kung Fu really is through a series of duels with the seven Japanese martial artists who come to meet the challenge!

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: Men From The Monastery
programme.desc: At the end of the Ming Dynasty, Wu San Gui betrays his people to the Qing officials and recruits fighters from all backgrounds. Members from Wudan and Ermei are the first to yield and collude with local bullies. When they start attacking the Shaolin Monastery, its most famous disciples have to band together and fight against the enemies.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: The Pirate
programme.desc: Pirate Chang Pao Chai discovers a leak in his ship after a successful raid on a foreign merchant ship. He goes ashore to get materials to patch up his ship, but encounters corrupt Qing officials oppressing the poor peasants. A good man at heart, he decides to help the peasants and gain a reputation of being a great pirate in the process.

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: A crippled billionaire mails a letter to each of his long-lost daughters inviting them to go to Japan, in the hope that he will find a worthy heir to inherit his vast fortune. The sisters finally meet abroad the plane to Japan, and one of them is taken with a man who is going to investigate the death of his lawyer uncle in a mysterious hit-and-run.

programme.title: The Assassin
programme.desc: Notorious assassin Nieh Cheng has retired into hiding. However, when Premier Yen's family is massacred, he seeks out the reclusive swordsman and coaxes him into a final revenge mission in this epic story set in the Six Kingdom era.

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Based on the classic Ming Dynasty novel The Water Margin, Three Sinners is a Huangmei Opera about love, betrayal, murder, and redemption. Starring Hong Kong's premiere movie couple, it is one of the grandest Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musicals in the Shaw Brothers library.

programme.title: The Blood Brothers
programme.desc: The friendship of three sworn brothers, Zhang, Huang and Ma ends when Ma gives in to corruption and falls for Huang's wife, eventually leading to a bloody ending.

programme.title: Les Belles
programme.desc: Acknowledged as one of the greatest Hong Kong musicals, this lavish movie starring Linda Lin, who won Best Actress for her performance, infuses its wispy plot with style and wit, and the results are pure pleasure.

programme.title: Shaolin Temple
programme.desc: As more people are learning martial arts from Shaolin, the Qing court orders for it to be banned and plans to destroy the temple. The Shaolin disciples decide to take their protest to the streets, using Shaolin skills to curb their hatred, but when the Qing troops start attacking Shaolin Temple, the disciples vow to protect it at all costs.

programme.title: The 82 Tenants
programme.desc: Continuing the success of the classic comedy House of 72 tenants, this sequel tells the stories of tenants living in an old building in Hong Kong who are forced to evict by the developers. Some tenants prefer to take the compensation while some resist the move. Will the acquisitions plan destroy the harmony of the neighborhood?

programme.title: Mercenaries From Hong Kong
programme.desc: Filmmaker Wong Jing produced Mercenaries From Hong Kong, his very first modern-day adventure drama. In the dramatic plot he wrote, he sends superstars Ti Lung, Chen Hui-min, Wang Lung-wei, Lo Lieh and Wang Yu on a deadly mission. The film's action sequences are all closely guided by three great kung fu choreographers, led by Tang Chia!

programme.title: Return Of The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This sequel makes for more bittersweet laughs and heart-wrenching misfortune, as Ah Niu gets out of the jail to find his true love becoming the wife of an abusive husband, and his uncle further exploits his naive nature.

programme.title: The Lizard
programme.desc: A seasoned burglar 'The Lizard' sets himself up against a corrupt police chief and announced that he will steal a diamond from a rich mans party. His real identity, which is discovered by the corrupt police chiefs granddaughter, is actually a young policeman who is doing it all for justice.

programme.title: Asia-Pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: The Casino
programme.desc: After being separated for many years, two childhood lovers meet in a possibly mythical "Lucky Casino" and vow to rid the establishment of the corrupt military generals, criminals and extortionists!

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: The Wandering Swordsman
programme.desc: The wandering swordsman Yu Hsieh Erh has formidable sword skills and helps the poor by robbing from thieves and distributing the wealth. He meets a group of bandits who are planning to rob a convoy escorting some valuables and is tricked into participating in the robbery. Yu soon realizes his folly and returns to take revenge on the bandits.

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: This film is an amusing insiders look at the Hong Kong film industry and is based on Director Li Han Hsiangs popular newspaper column recounting his work at Shaw Brothers. The collection of some of his funniest and most surreal film musings of the era, filled with behind-the-scene asides, this is a must-see for any Hong Kong cinema aficionado!

programme.title: Magnificent Wanderers
programme.desc: Lin and his two friends are traveling patriots who vow to stand up against violence and fight for justice. They meet a rich young man Chu by chance one day and the four become best friends. When a foreign prince plots to possess Chus family fortune and goes after him, Lin and friends go all out to help Chu fight against the villain.

programme.title: The Mirror And The Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: The Chinese Boxer
programme.desc: A Japanese karate master and Diao Er, who has been expelled from his martial arts school, return to the school to kill the school master and his disciples. After the massacre, disciple Lei Ming embarks on a vigorous training regime and vows to avenge their death. A fatal battle is about to begin

programme.title: Blue Skies
programme.desc: A young singer Hsiao Yun becomes an overnight sensation after standing in for another singer at the eleventh hour. Her success comes at a heavy price however, when her love with a pianist suffers. On top of this, Hsiao Yun must also deal with the unwanted affections from an influential backer of her show.

programme.title: The Mighty One
programme.desc: Lung seeks five volumes of a renowned Kung Fu manual to gain invincibility. When he believes a martial arts school master possesses the volumes, he kills him and his daughter but leaves behind a young brother and sister. Years later, Lung loses two volumes and starts another bloody hunt but each attempt is interrupted by two mysterious warriors...

programme.title: The Blue And The Black
programme.desc: Set during the Japanese occupation in World War II, a young orphan Tang Qi falls in a love with a young man Chang. However, their love is filled with challenges, from family pressure to the turmoil of war. When Tang Qi was raped, she is expelled from home to become a nightclub singer and embarks on a journey of no return

programme.title: Monkey Kung Fu
programme.desc: Wei Chun is a cocky young man sentenced to jail for killing a man in a fight. One day, Wei Chun picks a fight with a seemingly defenseless old man who completely thrashes him! The old man turns out to be the master of monkey style kung fu and as they become friends, he gives Wei Chun half of a medallion that would direct him to hidden secrets.

programme.title: The Voyage Of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung continues his incognito voyage to southern China. Accompanied by the minister and the imperial scholar, they have many amusing encounters in Yangzhou.

programme.title: The Fantastic Magic Baby
programme.desc: The story is about the legendary Monkey King (Liu Chung-chun) teams up with Goddess of Mercy (Chao Li-chuan) and the Dragon Girl (Lung Nu) to battle the child god Hung Hai-erh (Ting Hua-chung),son of the Ox Demon (Hung Hai-erh) to rescue Tang Tseng, the Holy Pilgrim (Teng Chio-jen).

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: The Sword Of Swords
programme.desc: The Sword Master passes on his sword to his disciple Lin before he dies. Another disciple Fang also eyes the sword and plots to take it away from Lin, destroying his family and blinding him in the process. Lin finally battles Fang for revenge and vows to reclaim his sword.

The real-life maritime disaster would inspire Herman Melville's Moby Dick. But that told only half the story. programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep4

programme.title: Rupert Bear Ep26
programme.desc: Rupert and the Weather Machine - When it starts raining sausages in Nutwood Rupert and friends fly up to the Cloud Shepherd's home to find out what has happened to the weather machine.

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep51
programme.desc: Why Are Acorns Buried Under The Tree? - Jess and the puppies find a pile of acorns buried under a tree. The puppies want to play with them, but Jess thinks they should find out why the acorns are buried there first. That's the Big Question! Baa and Billie don't know Billie says she'd eat acorns rather than bury them! Jess goes off to see Mimi who's planting her conker to grow a chestnut tree. Jess wonders if someone planted the acorns to grown into an oak but Mimi doesn't think so. They'd need to be buried somewhere with more space to grow. Jess tries Willow who is storing apples for the winter. She explains that she'll eat the apples when food is scarce in the winter months. Jess wonders if someone is storing the acorns. He and the puppies go back to the tree and wait. Soon a Squirrel pops out from the tree and buries another acorn. Jess and the pups are glad they didn't play with the acorns. Squirrel's storing them for Winter. They've answered the question yippety yay!

programme.title: Guess with Jess Ep52
programme.desc: How Can I Sound Like Brown Bird? - Brown Bird sings a lovely song before leaving for winter migration. Jess would love to sound like Brown Bird then they could listen to her song all year round. But how can he sound like her? That's the Big Question. Billie and Baa suggest Jess sings but his singing voice doesn't sound like Brown Bird at all. Mimi tries to mimic Brown Bird by whistling but that's not the right sound either. Maybe if Jess makes a hooty sound by blowing through his paws? That's still not the right sound. Jess tells his friends that it's more of a whistley sound a bit like the wind whistling through the reeds at Horace's pond. So they go to the pond. Horace shows Jess how to blow through the reeds and it sounds just like Brown Bird. They've found the Answer. Yippety yay!

Their goal is to make the school extremely difficult by replacing all the teachers with Teachertron robots. Suffering under the new regime and without Mr. Krupp/Captain Underpants on hand to help, the boys hypnotize gym teacher Mr. Meaner and turn him into Sergeant Boxers to fight back.

But the mysterious figure has followed Po and tries to capture them, clearly a new threat to our team.

He keeps curling up into a ball and Jess thinks he must need help and wants to find out how he can make his little friend feel better. But it's only when his farmyard buddies who are busy playing 'Scarey Steps' come and shout 'Scarey!' that Jess realises little HH curles up when he's frightened. Jess says goodbye and asks the children to see if they can spot a hedgehog out and about, but of course, remember to be gentle.
